# URBAN HUB LEAD MANAGEMENT SYSTEM - PROJECT CONTEXT

## PROJECT OVERVIEW
This is a comprehensive lead management system for Urban Hub with the following key modules:
- Lead Management (Hot, Cold, Dead, Converted leads)
- Student Management & Applications
- Studio Management
- Tourist Management
- Finance & Payment Processing
- Maintenance & Cleaning
- Analytics & Reporting

## CURRENT SYSTEM STATE
- Built with React + TypeScript + Vite
- Uses Supabase for database and authentication
- Tailwind CSS for styling with shadcn/ui components
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Live database integration (no mock data)

## CRITICAL REMINDERS
- This is a production system - always use live data
- Mobile responsiveness is paramount (10-12px fonts, 14-18px titles)
- All CRUD operations must work with real database
- UI/UX consistency across all modules is essential
- Back buttons must be positioned on the far right
- Dialog boxes need 2 close buttons and minimal padding
- Form validations are mandatory for all inputs

## TECHNICAL STACK
- Frontend: React 18, TypeScript, Vite
- Styling: Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui
- Database: Supabase (PostgreSQL)
- Authentication: Supabase Auth
- Payments: Stripe integration
- State Management: React Context + hooks
- File Handling: Supabase Storage

## DEVELOPMENT WORKFLOW
1. Always assess database schema first
2. Build on existing components and layouts
3. Ensure mobile responsiveness
4. Test CRUD operations with live data
5. Validate form inputs and user flows
6. Check intermodule communication
7. Verify no broken links or permissions
